Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,==========正文==========
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.99,0:01:43.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打开玲子的遗物干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.02,0:01:44.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.56,0:01:47.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  倒不是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.33,0:01:49.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知不觉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.00,0:01:53.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知不觉  一如既往地让人搞不懂的家伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.61,0:01:56.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粘上了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.35,0:02:00.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西瓜籽  嘴两边  两粒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.92,0:02:02.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别在意  不知不觉而已
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.47,0:02:04.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不明白你的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.51,0:02:07.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次还给妖怪名字
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.72,0:02:13.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲子的记忆成为思念  注入我的内心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.72,0:02:17.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲子这个人  一点点地…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.60,0:02:30.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向图书馆借的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.61,0:02:32.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来是忘记还了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.87,0:02:36.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,车票？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.47,0:02:46.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.62,0:02:49.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听我说  夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.43,0:02:52.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得是哪方错了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.09,0:02:57.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙说油炸豆腐清汤面里的豆腐是先吃的  难以置信吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.06,0:02:59.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是先吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.19,0:03:01.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.56,0:03:05.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豆腐是要浸在汤汁里最后吃的  是吧夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.40,0:03:09.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对  豆腐是要趁甜味没有被汤汁冲淡前吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.11,0:03:11.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样的吧  夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.73,0:03:15.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…我是觉得怎么都可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.39,0:03:16.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.39,0:03:17.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豆腐要后吃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.81,0:03:19.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豆腐要先吃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.98,0:03:23.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这么争论之前  那个不叫豆腐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.41,0:03:28.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个怎么都行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.84,0:03:29.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.50,0:03:30.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是后吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.20,0:03:31.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先吃对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.00,0:03:32.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  住手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.21,0:03:33.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝交
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.92,0:03:35.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  正和我意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.14,0:03:40.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无聊的争吵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.05,0:03:43.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给  你掉的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.73,0:03:48.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是过去的车票吧  怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.83,0:03:50.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.83,0:03:53.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟夏目有什么关系呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.84,0:03:56.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有什么说道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.92,0:04:00.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这样…今早上学时捡到的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.20,0:04:02.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拙劣的谎言
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.19,0:04:08.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.47,0:04:10.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等会再好好问你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.30,0:04:17.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.84,0:04:20.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃也没用哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.27,0:04:21.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不是这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.25,0:04:23.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.53,0:04:25.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里…回家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.72,0:04:28.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是要去那张车票的站头吧  一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.82,0:04:31.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,车站在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.50,0:04:33.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才没看清楚  忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.28,0:04:34.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在附近吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.42,0:04:37.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fe128\fscx80\fscy92\fnDFPTFLeiSho-W5}笹{\r}田  你为什么这么…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.02,0:04:39.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.84,0:04:45.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  自上次的试胆大会以来  我真的想见个面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.10,0:04:46.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见谁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.91,0:04:49.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见谁  你真讨厌  这不明摆着的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.85,0:04:51.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞧  车来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.33,0:04:53.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们上车吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.79,0:04:55.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你掉东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.99,0:04:58.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.18,0:05:02.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掉什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.75,0:05:07.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本没掉东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.59,0:05:08.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔细看看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.93,0:05:09.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.19,0:05:10.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.37,0:05:11.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.17,0:05:14.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.56,0:05:17.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.81,0:05:21.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开走了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.99,0:05:25.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊  到底我掉了什么啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.41,0:05:28.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.29,0:05:50.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总算来了吗  真慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.94,0:05:51.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猫咪老师
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.23,0:05:58.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里已经不使用了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.80,0:06:03.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  好像很久之前就成为废线了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.72,0:06:05.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真凄凉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.93,0:06:09.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雾沼是在另一边吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.25,0:06:12.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过为什么玲子又…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.34,0:06:22.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.49,0:06:24.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么热还真亏它能睡着
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.17,0:06:31.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.51,0:06:36.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是玲子  终于来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.79,0:06:38.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.33,0:06:40.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  别搞错了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.14,0:06:42.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不是玲子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.93,0:06:44.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.37,0:06:49.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是玲子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.81,0:06:53.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  我不是玲子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.52,0:06:56.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师  想点办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.96,0:06:59.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在说什么都没用
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.56,0:07:02.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是什么坏东西  你就陪他玩一会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.11,0:07:04.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什  什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.00,0:07:06.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.61,0:07:08.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.89,0:07:15.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  玲子死了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.61,0:07:18.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能明白真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.77,0:07:22.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是孙子嘛  气味相似也不足为奇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.70,0:07:26.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用闻得这么细致入微
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.28,0:07:28.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  浓毛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.58,0:07:33.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说在这里等玲子  是不是有什么约定啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.60,0:07:36.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  她说会和我一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.59,0:07:38.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起去？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.70,0:07:39.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.50,0:07:48.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雾沼  玲子要和你一起去雾沼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.83,0:07:50.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  雾沼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.59,0:07:52.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.88,0:07:54.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.55,0:07:59.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗡嗡地叫  说「不会原谅你的」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.58,0:08:02.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是玲子就说「不行啊」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.77,0:08:04.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.62,0:08:08.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让这家伙来说明还真是为难呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.20,0:08:11.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许这家伙在友人帐上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.94,0:08:15.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把名字还给它的话  思念会传达给我们事由的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.04,0:08:16.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.21,0:08:17.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你名字是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.91,0:08:21.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字  我叫三都
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.67,0:08:22.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三都
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.38,0:08:25.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾之守护哟  昭显其名吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.09,0:08:44.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵架了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.59,0:08:48.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生气的是实栗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.64,0:08:52.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢那个叫实栗的妖怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.33,0:08:56.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最喜欢实栗了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.51,0:09:02.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是实栗说讨厌我  不想再见我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.19,0:09:05.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做错什么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.60,0:09:09.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不记得了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.70,0:09:15.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那实栗对你说了什么生气的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.13,0:09:23.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好像多少有点明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.36,0:09:24.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实栗生气的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.48,0:09:27.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办啊  玲子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.04,0:09:29.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实栗现在在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.01,0:09:31.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雾沼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.73,0:09:33.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雾沼  邻站的？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.79,0:09:39.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了  那我和你一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.48,0:09:42.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包在我身上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.46,0:09:49.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过今天天色已晚  明天再在此碰头吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.11,0:09:52.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲子  谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.15,0:09:56.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很痒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.95,0:09:57.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  三都
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.69,0:10:06.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  没能完成约定
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.45,0:10:11.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定是玲子有了什么不能来的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.69,0:10:14.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.39,0:10:19.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方可能已经不在等待了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.39,0:10:22.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不去一下是不会知道的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.27,0:10:27.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去  要完成玲子没做完的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.43,0:10:32.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过今天天色已晚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.27,0:10:35.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天放学后我过来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.07,0:10:38.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.59,0:10:46.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了  还是现在就动身吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.88,0:10:51.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋  轻易就答应
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.98,0:10:54.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雾沼附近可没有公交车通过
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.88,0:10:58.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道走过去要多久吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.30,0:11:01.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到那肯定天都黑了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.98,0:11:10.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来是白说了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.91,0:11:27.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  三都
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.59,0:11:31.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲子不来的话  你一个人不也可以去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.63,0:11:34.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么就这么傻等着
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.53,0:11:39.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为约好了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.44,0:11:41.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真傻  居然去问他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.11,0:11:51.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始变冷了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.36,0:11:54.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像山间的寒风在流入
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.49,0:11:56.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  三都
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.50,0:12:10.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要说这家伙是可爱呢还是烦人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.70,0:12:17.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三都
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.78,0:12:21.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见到实栗的话  准备怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.91,0:12:24.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么  没想过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.93,0:12:29.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想和好的话  得说点什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.79,0:12:32.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.85,0:12:38.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是别让他们见面比较好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.65,0:12:41.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许反而会变麻烦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.97,0:12:44.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.00,0:12:47.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三都  在到达之前
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.41,0:12:48.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想好要说些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.45,0:12:51.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.11,0:12:52.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.99,0:12:53.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.89,0:12:56.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.30,0:12:57.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.50,0:12:59.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是怨念
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.96,0:13:00.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怨念？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.47,0:13:10.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三都
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.02,0:13:15.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会原谅  不会原谅你的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.25,0:13:18.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.16,0:13:30.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.19,0:13:31.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓稳咯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.35,0:13:35.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师  那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.36,0:13:37.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标是三都
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.86,0:13:38.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.13,0:13:41.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来实栗被地灵附身了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.99,0:13:42.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被地灵…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.38,0:13:45.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为地灵喜好愤怒及仇恨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.38,0:13:49.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实栗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.44,0:13:51.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实栗对三都如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.42,0:13:54.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是不要去见对方为好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.37,0:14:00.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么做  夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.52,0:14:02.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实栗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.07,0:14:04.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.15,0:14:06.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变得怎样我都不管了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.88,0:14:10.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去啊  猫咪老师
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.92,0:14:12.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.65,0:14:33.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷啊  仿佛不是夏天
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.06,0:14:35.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是山间的寒风
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.87,0:14:36.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是怨念所致吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.38,0:14:40.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实栗  出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.03,0:14:45.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实栗  有话要跟你说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.68,0:14:53.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三都  实栗长什么样子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.17,0:14:56.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…小小的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.24,0:14:59.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小小的  是多小
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.01,0:15:09.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么小吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.03,0:15:19.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个大小啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.25,0:15:30.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是开玩笑的时候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.90,0:15:32.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么在  夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.50,0:15:36.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.49,0:15:45.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现形吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.34,0:15:59.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲇…鲇鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.03,0:16:01.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实栗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.14,0:16:02.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那就是实栗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.22,0:16:05.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分明是奇大无比啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.99,0:16:09.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办夏目  要说服它吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.21,0:16:18.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为我是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.54,0:16:24.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.30,0:16:35.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你小子  是夏目玲子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.50,0:16:40.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来得正好  把友人帐交出来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.57,0:16:45.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,友人帐在那里面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.15,0:16:52.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.14,0:16:54.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是玲子的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.29,0:16:56.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我  蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.18,0:17:01.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实栗  实栗  是我  三都
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.39,0:17:05.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我不好  快醒过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.16,0:17:09.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实栗  快回来  求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.40,0:17:10.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三都
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.65,0:17:12.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把友人帐给我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.33,0:17:15.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要  不给
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.62,0:17:16.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.27,0:17:44.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.12,0:17:47.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧  夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.94,0:17:50.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.20,0:17:51.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.43,0:17:54.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实栗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.38,0:18:00.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然很可怜  看来跟地灵一起消失在沼泽底了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.49,0:18:03.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三都
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.69,0:18:13.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊  到底搞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.35,0:18:16.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  三都你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.84,0:18:18.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实栗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.84,0:18:21.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  要干什么笨蛋  放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.36,0:18:22.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  住手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.96,0:18:24.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实栗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.57,0:18:27.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这样  很恶心啊  住手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.69,0:18:29.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说放开我了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.78,0:18:36.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么  吵架是因为玲子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.33,0:18:38.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  因为夏目玲子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.01,0:18:41.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.39,0:18:43.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.70,0:18:46.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这蠢货把重要的名字给了玲子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.22,0:18:48.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们吵架了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.23,0:18:52.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有作为妖怪的自尊吗  你这大蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.87,0:18:55.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来再也不想见你的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.61,0:18:58.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却又恬不知耻地出现了  你这呆瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.31,0:18:59.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.80,0:19:03.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  不用这么说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.90,0:19:07.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三都喜欢你  所以一直牵挂着
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.67,0:19:08.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说它蠢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.24,0:19:11.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有心道歉的话给我快点过来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.33,0:19:12.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直心不在焉的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.49,0:19:14.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.08,0:19:14.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.48,0:19:16.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.30,0:19:16.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  实栗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.65,0:19:18.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目  看仔细了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.20,0:19:21.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  有在听吗浓毛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.07,0:19:23.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在跟你说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.26,0:19:25.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.70,0:19:29.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这两个家伙  早就和好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.13,0:19:33.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实栗  我们回山里去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.23,0:19:34.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用你说也会回去的  你个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.48,0:19:39.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目  真的谢谢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.08,0:19:41.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋  别向人类低头
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.23,0:19:44.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  他把名字也还给我了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.32,0:19:46.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.72,0:19:50.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说别低头了  你这笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.21,0:20:02.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么  又不知不觉了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.86,0:20:04.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是把它放回原处啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.42,0:20:10.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说玲子没能完成约定是因为有特别的原因对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.62,0:20:13.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太瞧得起她了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.32,0:20:16.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是一不小心忘记了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.58,0:20:18.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲子就是这样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.19,0:20:20.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么随便…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.03,0:20:22.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么这书是怎么回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.99,0:20:26.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是借着没还吗  瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.64,0:20:33.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.29,0:20:35.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  看来忘了不少呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.45,0:20:39.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去真像是有特别原因呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.68,0:20:42.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  玲子啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.61,0:20:48.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.92,0:20:50.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早…早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.45,0:20:52.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看那边
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.24,0:20:55.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们和好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.66,0:21:01.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天那算是什么啊  真莫名其妙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.86,0:21:04.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  因为是好朋友嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.41,0:21:12.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  昨天怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.78,0:21:17.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  对了  想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.27,0:21:19.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失陪一下  这个拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.64,0:21:21.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.56,0:21:22.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fe128\fscx80\fscy92\fnDFPTFLeiSho-W5}笹{\r}田  {\fe128\fscx80\fscy92\fnDFPTFLeiSho-W5}笹{\r}田
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.43,0:21:27.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天妇罗面条里的虾  你是先吃还是后吃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.31,0:21:29.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种东西怎样都好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.41,0:21:37.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好朋友…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.95,0:21:43.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天  谢谢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.37,0:21:46.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到你很为难嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.83,0:23:38.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沉入了水坝的村子出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.05,0:23:42.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,栖身在那的妖怪们为了要回名字而来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.24,0:23:44.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你这家伙  别缠住夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.73,0:23:46.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想见一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.54,0:23:48.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂时要麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.91,0:23:50.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想见的人…
